ck, also Krper, Seele und Geist. Ich wnsche Ihnen viel Erfolg, Lebensfreude und vor allem Gesundheit.", "language": null, "image": "https://pocketbook.de/media/catalog/product/cache/6b1c09900b407c50fce2db5e66ebc123/f/3/f32e080b887ac241.jpg", "pagetype": "product", "links": ["https://pocketbook.de/de_de/", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/checkout/cart/", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/pocketbook_customer/personal/", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/wishlist/", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/customer/account/login/", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/", "#store.menu", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/ebooks", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/fiction", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/ebooks/books-for-children-young-readers", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/textbooks", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/counselor", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/ebooks/travels", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/non-fiction", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/fiction/fantasy-science-fiction", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/fiction/mystery-thriller", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/ebooks/preisaktionen", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/ebooks/top-10-ebooks", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/e-books/spiegel-bestseller", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/fiction", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/books-for-children-young-readers", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/textbooks", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/counselor", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/travels", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/non-fiction", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/fiction/fantasy-science-fiction", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/fiction/humor-comic-satire", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/fiction/mystery-thriller", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/fiction/novels-stories", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/fiction/novels-stories/historical-novels", "https://pocketbook.de/de_de/horbucher/books-for-children-young-readers/ne